author: kmenard
msg: Fixed CAY-671: custom exception class for ROP missing session

Applied Tore's patch from the JIRA comments and added an appropriate test.  All CayenneRuntimeExceptions from the server are not wrapped again on the client.  If this is problematic for people, we can do it more selectively (e.g., just for MissingSessionException).
